  "texts": [
    "A network was fitted with an additional layer that could extract the relevant visual features and latent dimensions to provide recommendations.",
    "In the field of fashion recommendation, the style of a fashion item also has a significant impact on customer preference.",
    "Liu et al. (2017) proposed a method called DeepStyle (Liu et al. 2017) to characterize user preferences by learning the style features of items.",
    "As shown in Fig. 10, the style features was obtained by subtracting item category features from visual features.",
    "Style features were then integrated into the widely used BPR (Rendle et al. 2012) framework to generate fashion recommendations."
